{"tid":1810073,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唔想輸入黎推呢個！！！","createTime":"2020-01-03T14:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T15:04:02.000Z","uid":4586,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"96a1da68c0020efb0efba120e2c1febd2fb2eaf8","tid":1810073,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:12:05.000Z","msg":"今日撞到個中同<br />\n我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n：最近有咩搞<br />\n：岩岩去完歐遊<br />\n呢度我已經慶慶地<br />\n：前線打生打死你仲有心情玩？<br />\n：咁有人中槍 我洗咪中夠兩槍<br />\n：前線唔係condom<br />\n：咁劫獄囉 失敗最少多個朋友一齊mou<br />\n：兄弟爬山 你最少做下文宣啦 咩都唔做一定一齊輸<br />\n：咁我係屋企用念力撚死差佬囉<br />\n呢刻我完全忍唔到，即刻出拳私了佢。<br />\n最後俾佢打都仆街，但真係唔關佢腹肌事。<br />\n唯有影左佢大頭，夠50正評我開佢樣批鬥。"},{"pid":"b66543999d053053ade1caab6853e82be79a216c","tid":1810073,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"樓主先喺岩岩去完歐遊果個，而家比人打完仲想貼人出黎"},{"pid":"6dfb91a7661cd4a74900fec2682f917f5bd464a2","tid":1810073,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66543999d053053ade1caab6853e82be79a216c","tid":1810073,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"樓主先喺岩岩去完歐遊果個，而家比人打完仲想貼人出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d714bd9a0511439de0f95f7dde2ad3c53bee08a","tid":1810073,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dfb91a7661cd4a74900fec2682f917f5bd464a2","tid":1810073,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66543999d053053ade1caab6853e82be79a216c","tid":1810073,"uid":5649,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:17:49.000Z","msg":"樓主先喺岩岩去完歐遊果個，而家比人打完仲想貼人出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T14:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm